content:
print("What is the image you want to have? (Image Address)")
local image = read()
local monitor = peripheral.wrap("top")
monitor.setTextScale(0.5)
local SizeX, SizeY = monitor.getSize()
SizeX = SizeX * 2
SizeY = SizeY * 3
local image = http.post(
    "https://computercraftimage.enderreaper64.repl.co/post", 
    '{"Image":"' .. image .. '", "SizeX":' .. tostring(SizeX) .. ', "SizeY":' .. tostring(SizeY) .. '}', 
    {["Content-Type"] = "application/json"}
)

shell.run("wget https://github.com/9551-Dev/apis/raw/main/pixelbox_lite.lua")

local imageData = image.readAll()
local count = 0
local count2 = 1
os.loadAPI("json")

local data = json.decode(imageData)
for a,b in pairs(data[1][1]) do
    monitor.setPaletteColor(2^(a-1), tonumber(b))
    print(a-1, tonumber(b), b)
end

local box = require("pixelbox_lite").new(monitor)

for y = 1, SizeY do
    for x = 1, SizeX do
        box.CANVAS[y][x] = 2^tonumber(data[1][2][tostring(y-1)][tostring(x-1)])
    end
end

box:render()

LWE persona generator
content:
---
# Persona generator.yaml
- name: Persona generator
  hosts: localhost
  gather_facts: no
  vars:
    url: "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/daveshap/Automated_Consensus/main/persona_traits.json"
    iterations: 10
    output_dir: "/tmp/personas"

  tasks:
    - name: "Retrieve JSON persona data from URL: {{ url }}"
      uri:
        url: "{{ url }}"
        return_content: yes
      register: result

    - name: Convert JSON data to usable format
      set_fact:
        data: "{{ result.content | from_json }}"

    - name: Loop to generate personas
      loop: "{{ range(1, iterations + 1) }}"
      loop_control:
        loop_var: iteration
      vars:
        iteration: "{{ item }}"
      include_tasks: persona-generator-create-persona.yaml
...

---
# persona-generator-create-persona.yaml
- name: Output current iteration
  debug:
    msg: "Iteration: {{ iteration }}"

- name: "Initialize characteristics list for persona {{ iteration }}"
  set_fact:
    characteristics: []

- name: "Loop over keys in JSON data for persona {{ iteration }}"
  loop: "{{ data.keys() | list }}"
  loop_control:
    loop_var: key
  vars:
    key: "{{ item }}"
  include_tasks: persona-generator-create-characteristics.yaml

- name: "Format characteristics for persona {{ iteration }}"
  set_fact:
    characteristics_string: "{{ characteristics | join('\n') }}"

- name: "Output assembled characteristics for persona {{ iteration }}"
  debug:
    msg: |
      CHARACTERISTICS:

      {{ characteristics_string }}

- name: "Generate persona {{ iteration }} using LLM"
  lwe_llm:
    message: |
      Generate a 100-200 word persona for someone with the following characteristics:

      {{ characteristics_string }}
  register: llm_result
  until: llm_result is succeeded
  delay: 10
  retries: 3

- name: "Output generated persona {{ iteration }}"
  debug:
    msg: |
      PERSONA:

      {{ llm_result.response }}

- name: "Store characteristics and persona in file for persona {{ iteration }}"
  copy:
    dest: "{{ output_dir }}/persona-{{ iteration }}"
    content: |
      CHARACTERISTICS:

      {{ characteristics_string }}

      PERSONA:

      {{ llm_result.response }}
...

---
# persona-generator-create-characteristics.yaml
- name: "Pick random value for characteristic: {{ key }}"
  set_fact:
    value: "{{ data[key] | random }}"

- name: Add key-value pair to characteristics list
  set_fact:
    characteristics: "{{ characteristics + [key + ': ' + value] }}"
...

Show notification when workspace changes for XFCE
content:
#!/bin/bash
# Description: Show notification when workspace changes for XFCE
# Requires: awk, xfce4-notifyd, libnotify, wmctrl

sleep 3
WKS_NUMBER=$(wmctrl -d | awk -v val='*' '$2==val{print $1}')

while true
do
  WKS_NUMBER_NEW=$(wmctrl -d | awk -v val='*' '$2==val{print $1}')
  if [ ${WKS_NUMBER} -ne ${WKS_NUMBER_NEW} ]; then
    WKS_NUMBER=${WKS_NUMBER_NEW}
    WKS_NAME=$(wmctrl -d | awk -v val='*' '$2==val{print $10}')
    NUM_DISPLAY=$(( ${WKS_NUMBER} + 1 ))
    notify-send -t 2000 -i cs-workspaces "Workspace Changed" "Workspace changed to \"${WKS_NAME}\" [${NUM_DISPLAY}]"
  fi
  sleep 0.5
done

exit 0

local robot = require('robot')
local computer = require('computer')
local event = require('event')
local fs = require("filesystem")
local term = require('term')
local serial = require('serialization')
local com = require('component')
local sides = require('sides')
local rssignal

-- Безопасная подгрузка компонентов
local function safeLoadComponents(name)
  if com.isAvailable(name) then
    return com.getPrimary(name), true
  else
    return 'ERROR! Компонент '..name..' не найден!', false
  end
end
 
-- ===== Всякие принтилки, писалки на экран разной кучи инфы и всякие проверки =====

-- проверка компонентов
local tun, state_tun = safeLoadComponents('tunnel')
local rs, state_redstone = safeLoadComponents('redstone')
local icontroller, state_icontroller = safeLoadComponents('inventory_controller')	
local magnet, state_magnet = safeLoadComponents('tractor_beam')
local sign, state_sign = safeLoadComponents('sign')

term.clear()
print('-------------------------------------------------')
print('       Универсальная многоцелевая программа      ')
print('    для ручного управления роботом с планшета!   ')
print('          проект http://mcskill.net              ')
print('                                                 ')
print('-------------------------------------------------')
print('Рекомендуемые аппаратные требования:')
print('ЦП / ОЗУ:    - 3 ур. / 1 Мб')
print('Сеть:        - связанная карта (обязательно)')
print('Размер инв.: - 16+ слотов')
print('Апгрейды:    - контроллер инвентаря (обязательно)')
print('магнит, редстоун-карта, апгрейд Табличка I/O')
print('Опционально: ЧЛ и др. (пока не реализовано)')
print('-------------------------------------------------')
term.write('Нажмите ENTER для продолжения...')
io.read()
term.clear()
		print('=============  Проверка компонентов  ===========')
		if not state_tun then
					print (tun)
					print('ВНИМАНИЕ! Аппаратные возможности Вашего робота')
					print('не удовлетворяют миним. требованиям программы!')
					print('Установите в робота тоннельную (связанную) карту для максимально комфортной работы.')
					print('=================================================')
					print ('Программа завершена.')
					os.exit()
				else
					print('Тоннельная карта:      ОК ')
		end
		if not state_icontroller then
					print (icontroller)
					print('ВНИМАНИЕ! Аппаратные возможности Вашего робота')
					print('не удовлетворяют миним. требованиям программы!')
					print('Установите в робота контроллер инвентаря!')
					print('=================================================')
					print ('Программа завершена.')
					os.exit()
				else
					print('Контроллер инвентаря:  ОК ')
		end
		if not state_redstone then
					print (rs)
					print('Аппаратные возможности робота ограничены!')
					print('Вы не сможете управлять редстоун сигналами!')
					rssignal = 'редстоун НЕ УСТ.'
				else
					print('Красная карта:         ОК ')
					rssignal = 'редстоун выкл.'
					rs.setOutput(sides.front, 0)
					rs.setOutput(sides.bottom, 0)
					rs.setOutput(sides.top, 0)
		end
		if not state_magnet then
					print(magnet)
					print('Аппаратные возможности робота ограничены!')
					print('Вы не сможете подбирать лут с земли!')
				else
					print('Магнит апгрейд:        ОК ')
		end
		if not state_sign then
					print (sign)
					print('Аппаратные возможности робота ограничены!')
					print('Вы не сможете писать на табличках!')
				else
					print('Апгрейд Табличка I/O:  ОК ')
		end
		print('=================================================')
		term.write('Нажмите ENTER для продолжения...')
		io.read()


-- Константы
local MAXPACKET = tun.maxPacketSize()
local INVSIZE = robot.inventorySize()
local MAX_EU  = computer.maxEnergy()
local TOTAL_MEM = computer.totalMemory()/1024
local neon = {0x0000ff,0x00ff00,0xffff00,0x00ffff,0xff00c0,0xff0000, 0x000000}

-- Переменные
local DYNAMIC_VIEW = true
local current_neon = 1
local robot_status = 'Ожидаю команд...'

local  function sendData(array)
  local data = serial.serialize(array)
  tun.send(data)
end

local function getEU()
	return math.floor(computer.energy())
end

local function freeMEM()
	return math.floor(computer.freeMemory()/1024)
end

local  function  printStatus()
	term.clear()
	print('==================== Статус =====================')
	print('Имя робота:            '..robot.name())
	print('Уровень прокачки:      '..robot.level())
	print('Всего/свободно слотов: '..INVSIZE..'/'..'нет данных')
	print('Ёмкость батареи:       '..MAX_EU..' EU')
	print('Текущий заряд:         '..getEU()..' EU')
	print('Всего RAM:             '..TOTAL_MEM..' KБ')
	print('Свободно RAM:          '..freeMEM()..' KБ')
	print('Время работы/RS:       '..math.floor(computer.uptime()/60)..' мин./'..rssignal)
	print('=================================================')
	print('Данные Wi-Fi:  ', robot_status)
end
-- формирование и отправка данных о роботе (параметры, инвентарь и прочее)
local  function infoStatSend()
	local full_info = {
	'infoRobot', 
	'Имя робота/уровень прокачки:     '..robot.name()..'/'..robot.level(),
	'Всего/свободно слотов:           '..INVSIZE..'/нет данных',
	'Ёмкость батареи/текущий заряд:   '..MAX_EU..'/'..getEU()..' EU',
	'Всего/cвободно RAM:              '..TOTAL_MEM..'/'..freeMEM()..' KБ',
	'Время работы/редстоун:           '..math.floor(computer.uptime()/60)..' мин./'..rssignal,
	'  --- Перечень предметов в слотах (слот, имя, кол-во) ---'
	}
	for i=1, INVSIZE do
		local amount = robot.count(i)
		if amount > 0 then
      		robot.select(i)
			stack = icontroller.getStackInInternalSlot(i)
      		local data_item = i..': '..stack.label..' - '..amount..' шт.'
      		table.insert(full_info, data_item)	
    	end
  	end
  	sendData(full_info)
end

local  function infoStatSendDynamicView()
	if DYNAMIC_VIEW == true then infoStatSend() end
end

-- =====  таблица действий робота на сетевые команды  ======
local list = {

		--движение робота
		['w'] = function() robot.forward() end,
		['s']= function() robot.back() end,
		['d']= function() robot.turnRight() end,
		['a']= function() robot.turnLeft() end,
		['lshift']= function() robot.up() end,
		['lcontrol']= function() robot.down() end,

		--дейстия сверху ЛКМ, ПКМ, Shift-ПКМ
		['i']= function() robot.swingUp() end,
		['o']= function() robot.useUp() end,
		['p']= function() robot.useUp(sides.top, true) end,

		--дейстия спереди ЛКМ, ПКМ, Shift-ПКМ
		['q']= function() robot.swing() end,
		['e']= function() robot.use() end,
		['r']= function() robot.use(sides.front, true) end,

		--дейстия снизу ЛКМ, ПКМ, Shift-ПКМ
		['j']= function() robot.swingDown() end,
		['k']= function() robot.useDown() end,
		['l']= function() robot.useDown(sides.bottom, true) end,

		--======команды 0-9=================
		--ВЫБРОСИТЬ ВСЕ и выбрать 1-й слот
		['1']= function() 
				for i=1, INVSIZE do
					if robot.count(i) > 0 then
			      		robot.select(i)
			      		robot.drop()
			      		infoStatSendDynamicView() 
			      	end
		      	end
		      	robot.select(1)
		end,

		--собрать весь дроп с земли, пока могу это делать!
		['2']= function() 
				if not state_magnet then return end
		  		robot.select(1)	
		    	while magnet.suck()  do
		    		infoStatSendDynamicView() 
		    	end
		end,

		-- ВЗЯТЬ из сундука СВЕРХУ
		['3']= function() 
				robot.select(1)	
				robot.suckUp() 
				infoStatSendDynamicView() 
		end,

		-- ВЗЯТЬ из сундука СПЕРЕДИ
		['4']= function() 
				robot.select(1)	
				robot.suck() 
				infoStatSendDynamicView()
		end,

		-- ВЗЯТЬ из сундука СНИЗУ
		['5']= function() 
				robot.select(1)	
				robot.suckDown() 
				infoStatSendDynamicView() 
		end,

		-- Что вокруг меня?
		['6']= function()
		local scan = {'scan'}
				if robot.detect() then
					table.insert(scan,'     Cпереди - БЛОК')
				else
					table.insert(scan,'     Cпереди - 0')
				end
				if robot.detectUp() then
					table.insert(scan,'     Cверху  - БЛОК')
				else
					table.insert(scan,'     Cверху  - 0')
				end
				if robot.detectDown() then
					table.insert(scan,'     Cнизу   - БЛОК')
				else
					table.insert(scan,'     Cнизу   - 0')
				end
				robot.turnRight()
				if robot.detect() then
					table.insert(scan,'     Cправа  - БЛОК')
				else
					table.insert(scan,'     Cправа  - 0')
				end
				robot.turnRight()
				if robot.detect() then
					table.insert(scan,'     Сзади   - БЛОК')
				else
					table.insert(scan,'     Сзади   - 0')
				end
				robot.turnRight()
				if robot.detect() then
					table.insert(scan,'     Слева   - БЛОК')
				else
					table.insert(scan,'     Слева   - 0')
				end
				robot.turnRight()
				sendData(scan)
		end,

		-- Выбрать слот N
		['7']= function(data) pcall(robot.select, tonumber(data[2])) end,

		--Дроп текущего слота
		['8']= function() robot.drop() end,

		--показать статистику
		['9']= function() infoStatSend() end,

		--поставить блок Сверху
		['z']= function() robot.placeUp() end,

		--поставить блок Спереди
		['x']= function() robot.place() end,

		--поставить блок Снизу
		['c']= function() robot.placeDown() end,

		--включить/выключить редстоун излучение
		['f']= function() 
				if not state_redstone then return end
				if rssignal == 'редстоун выкл.' then
					rs.setOutput(sides.front, 15)
					rs.setOutput(sides.bottom, 15)
					rs.setOutput(sides.top, 15)
					rssignal = 'редстоун вкл.'
				else
					rs.setOutput(sides.front, 0)
					rs.setOutput(sides.bottom, 0)
					rs.setOutput(sides.top, 0)
					rssignal = 'редстоун выкл.'
				end	
		end,
		--цикличная смена цвета неоновой подсветки робота
		['n']= function()
				if current_neon > #neon then
					current_neon = 1
				end
				robot.setLightColor(neon[current_neon])
				current_neon =  current_neon + 1
		end,

		-- вкл./выкл. показа динамического изменения инвентаря робота
		['v']= function() DYNAMIC_VIEW = not DYNAMIC_VIEW end,

		--меняем инструмент на инструмент в активном слоте инвентаря
		['y']= function() if not state_icontroller then return end icontroller.equip() end,

		--пишем текст на табличках
		['t']= function(data) 
				if not state_sign then return end 
				sign.setValue(tostring(data[2])) 
	end

}


local  function  main()
	robot.select(1)
	printStatus()
	while true do
		--ожидаем команд (события) по wi-fi, каждые 30 сек - срыв ожидания и принт статуса
		e, _, _, _, _, msg  = event.pull(30,'modem_message')
	    if e then
	    	robot_status = msg
	    	printStatus()
		    data = serial.unserialize(msg)
			--если существует ключ, вызываем действие из массива и передаем все данные из сообщения
			if list[data[1]] then
				list[data[1]](data) 
			end
		else 
			-- ничего не делаем, курим, принтим на экран инфу о разряжающейся батарейке:)
			printStatus()
		end	
	end
end

main()

content:
import os
import codecs
import time
import random
from ascii_art import *
from weapons import *
from characters import *
import sys

colors = {
    "black": "\033[30m",
    "red": "\033[31m",
    "green": "\033[32m",
    "yellow": "\033[33m",
    "blue": "\033[34m",
    "magenta": "\033[35m",
    "cyan": "\033[36m",
    "white": "\033[37m",
    "orange": "\033[38;5;208m",
    "reset": "\033[0m",
    "white_on_green": "\033[37;42m",
    "white_on_blue": "\033[37;44m",
    "black_on_yellow": "\033[30;43m",
    "yellow_on_red": "\033[33;41m",
    "white_on_red": "\033[37;41m",
}

BAR_CHAR = "█"
EMPTY_BAR_CHAR = "▓"

DELAY = 0.025 # set to 0.035 for standard starting speed

strings = {}

working_dir = os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__))

def cursor_style(int):
    """Changes command line interface / terminal cursor style

    Args:
        int (int): integer value
        
    Styles:
        6: steady vertical bar
        5: blinking vertical bar
        4: steady underscore
        3: blinking underscore
        2: steady block
        1: blinking block
        0 / else: reset to terminal default
    """
    if 1 <= int <= 6:
        sys.stdout.write(f'\033[{int} q')
    else:
        # reset to terminal default
        sys.stdout.write('\033[0 q')

def print_separator():
    print("» «" * 25 + "\n")

def banner(phrase, color_style):
    """
    Displays centered text in a banner style, 1 bar.
    """
    console_width = 60
    spaces = ((console_width - len(phrase)) //2)
    centered_text = " " * spaces + phrase
    length = console_width - len(centered_text)
    centered_text = centered_text + " " * length
    delay_print(f"{colors[color_style]}{centered_text}{colors['reset']}\n")
    return None

def menu(phrase, color_style):
    """
    Displays centered text in a menu style, 3 bars.
    """
    console_width = 60
    spaces = ((console_width - len(phrase)) //2)
    centered_text = " " * spaces + phrase
    length = console_width - len(centered_text)
    centered_text = centered_text + " " * length
    print(f"{colors[color_style]}{' ' * console_width}")
    print(f"{centered_text}")
    print(f"{' ' * console_width}{colors['reset']}")

    return None

def change_print_speed():
    current_speed = DELAY
    speed = float(input(f"Current speed is {colors['orange']}{current_speed}{colors['reset']}. New text speed: "))
    update_delay(speed)
    delay_print(f"Print speed changed to {colors['orange']}{speed}{colors['reset']}. This is an example of how fast the text will print.\n",DELAY)


def update_delay(speed):
    global DELAY
    DELAY = speed
    


def delay_print(text, delay=DELAY):
    for char in text:
        print(char, end='', flush=True)
        time.sleep(DELAY)


def clear_screen():
    if os.name == 'nt':
        os.system('cls')
    else:
        os.system('clear')
    # print("\033[2J") # Use ansi escape instead


def load_strings(filename):
    with open(filename, "r") as file:
        for line in file:
            if line.strip():
                if "=" not in line:
                    print(f"Unexpected line format: {line}")
                    continue
                key, value = line.strip().split("=", 1)
                value = codecs.decode(value, 'unicode_escape')
                strings[key] = value.replace("\\n", "\n")

def print_string(key, **kwargs):
    string = strings.get(key, "<MISSING>")
    fstring = string.format(**kwargs)
    delay_print(fstring, DELAY)
    print()
    

def health_bar(target):
    health_percentage = round((target.health / target.max_health) * 100)
    if health_percentage >= 75:
        color = colors['green']
    elif health_percentage >= 50:
        color = colors['yellow']
    elif health_percentage >= 25:
        color = colors['orange']
    else:
        color = colors['red']
    health_bar = BAR_CHAR * target.health
    health_bar += EMPTY_BAR_CHAR * (target.max_health - target.health)

    health_bar = BAR_CHAR * int(health_percentage / 10)
    empty_bar = EMPTY_BAR_CHAR * (10 - int(health_percentage / 10))
    
    print(f"{colors['yellow']}{target.name}{colors['reset']}'s Health: {color}{health_percentage}% {health_bar}{colors['white']}{empty_bar}{colors['reset']}")


def xp_bar(player):
    if player.level < 10:
        xp_percentage = round((player.xp / (player.level * 25)) * 100)
        # xp_bar = BAR_CHAR * player.xp
        # xp_bar += EMPTY_BAR_CHAR * ((player.level * 25) - player.xp)
        xp_bar = BAR_CHAR * int(xp_percentage / 10)
        xp_bar += EMPTY_BAR_CHAR * (10 - int(xp_percentage / 10))
        print(f"XP: {colors['cyan']}{xp_percentage}% {xp_bar}{colors['reset']}")
        
        if player.level < 10:
            if xp_percentage == 100: # level up character
                Character.level_up(player)
                print_separator()
                delay_print(f"{colors['white_on_blue']} »»» »»» »»» YOU HAVE REACHED LEVEL {player.level}! ««« ««« ««« {colors['reset']}\n")
                delay_print(f"(This would be a good time to {colors['blue']}visit the store{colors['reset']} in town.)\n")
                print_separator()

def list_save_files(directory):
    save_files = []
    for filename in os.listdir(directory):
        if filename.endswith(".sav"):
            save_files.append(filename)
    return save_files


def load_game(load_name):
    if not os.path.isfile(load_name):
        delay_print("Save file not found!\n",DELAY)
        input("Press enter to continue.")
        return None

    with open(load_name, "r") as file:
        player_data = {}
        for line in file:
            key, value = line.strip().split("=")
            player_data[key] = value

        name = player_data.get("Name", "")
        level = int(player_data.get("Level", 1))
        health = int(player_data.get("Health", 0))
        xp = int(player_data.get("XP", 0))
        gold = int(player_data.get("Gold", 0))
        weapon_name = player_data.get("Weapon", "")
        armor_name = player_data.get("Armor","")
        speed=float((player_data.get("Speed",0.025)))
        update_delay(speed)

        player = Character(name)
        player.level = level
        player.health = health
        player.max_health = player.level * 30
        player.xp = xp
        player.gold = gold

        for weapon_list in weapons_by_level.values():
            for weapon in weapon_list:
                if weapon.name == weapon_name:
                    player.weapon = weapon
                    break
                
        for armor_list in armor_by_level.values():
            for armor in armor_list:
                if armor.name == armor_name:
                    player.armor = armor
                    break

        return player
    

def save_game(player):
    save_name = working_dir + "/" + player.name + ".sav"
    with open(save_name, "w") as file:
        file.write(f"Name={player.name}\n")
        file.write(f"Level={player.level}\n")
        file.write(f"Health={player.health}\n")
        file.write(f"XP={player.xp}\n")
        file.write(f"Gold={player.gold}\n")
        file.write(f"Weapon={player.weapon.name}\n")
        file.write(f"Armor={player.armor.name}\n")
        file.write(f"Speed={DELAY}\n")

def decide_first_strike(player, enemy):
    # this function chooses randomly who attacks first: player or enemy
    return random.choice([player, enemy])

def combat(player):
    # get an enemy of the same level as the player
    while True: # ensures no enemy spawns with zero health
        enemy = get_enemy(player.level)
        if enemy is None:
            print("No enemies found at this level.")
            return
        if enemy.health > 1:
            break
    print_separator()
    delay_print(f"\n{colors['yellow_on_red']} »» {colors['reset']} A {random.choice(adjectives)} {colors['cyan']}{enemy.name}{colors['reset']} ({enemy.health}) is attacking! {colors['yellow_on_red']} «« {colors['reset']}\n", DELAY)

    while player.health > 0 and enemy.health > 0:
        health_bar(player)
        health_bar(enemy)
        delay_print(f"\n({colors['yellow']}A{colors['reset']})ttack\n({colors['yellow']}H{colors['reset']})eal yourself\n({colors['yellow']}F{colors['reset']})lee to safety\n")
        choice = input(f"{player.name}, choose: ").upper()
        if choice == "A":
            # Decide who strikes first
            first_striker = decide_first_strike(player, enemy)
            if first_striker == player:
                if player.health > 0:
                    player_attack(player, enemy)
                if enemy.health > 0:
                    enemy_attack(player, enemy)
                    print()
            else:
                if enemy.health > 0:
                    enemy_attack(player, enemy)
                if player.health > 0:
                    player_attack(player, enemy)
                    print()
        elif choice == "H":
            try_healing(player)
        elif choice == "F":
            delay_print(f"You run away and wonder if the name {colors['cyan']}{player.name}{colors['reset']} will ever bring honor to your family.\n", DELAY)
            print_separator()
            return
    if player.health == 0:
        death(player)

    if enemy.health == 0:
        g = random.randint(1, (player.level * 5) + player.level)
        player.gain_gold(g)
        player.xp += 1
        banner(enemy.name + " has been slaughtered!","yellow_on_red")
        delay_print(f"You have gained valuable experience and {colors['yellow']}{g}{colors['reset']} gold!\n")
        print_separator()
        display_bars(player)
        save_game(player)
        return

def try_healing(player):
        heal_amount = player.max_health - player.health
        if heal_amount > 0:
            heal_cost = (heal_amount + (round(player.level * 1.5)))
            delay_print(f"You can heal {colors['yellow']}{heal_amount}{colors['reset']} damage points at a cost of {colors['yellow']}{heal_cost}{colors['reset']} gold.\n")
            choice = input("Do you want to proceed with healing? (Y/N): ").upper()
            if choice == "Y":
                if player.gold >= heal_cost:
                    player.heal(heal_amount)
                    player.lose_gold(heal_cost)
                    delay_print(f"You have healed {colors['yellow']}{heal_amount}{colors['reset']} damage points at a cost of {colors['yellow']}{heal_cost}{colors['reset']} gold.\n \n")
                    display_bars(player)
                else:
                    delay_print("You don't have enough gold to heal.\n")
            else:
                delay_print("You scoff at the thought of healing! You're too tough for that...\n")
        else:
            delay_print("You don't need healing at the moment.\n")

  
def player_attack(player, enemy):
    damage = random.randint(0, player.weapon.damage)
    if damage == 0:
        delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}»»{colors['reset']}In your haste and excitement, you miss {colors['cyan']}{enemy.name}{colors['reset']}. You burn with shame.\n", DELAY)
    else:
        damage = damage + (player.level * 3)
        enemy.take_damage(damage)
        delay_print(f"{colors['orange']}»»{colors['reset']}You attack {colors['cyan']}{enemy.name}{colors['reset']} with {colors['green']}{player.weapon.name}{colors['reset']} for {colors['orange']}{damage}{colors['reset']} damage!\n",DELAY)
        damage = 0 # empty damage for next round

def enemy_attack(player, enemy):
    damage = random.randint(0, enemy.damage)
    if damage == 0:
        delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}»» {colors['cyan']}{enemy.name}{colors['reset']} misses you completely.\n", DELAY)
    else:
        defense = random.randint(0,player.armor.defense)
        if defense >= damage:
            delay_print(f"{colors['red']}»» {colors['cyan']}{enemy.name}{colors['reset']}'s attack is absorbed by your {colors['green']}{player.armor.name}{colors['reset']}!\n", DELAY)
        else:
            player.take_damage(damage - defense)
            delay_print(f"{colors['red']}»» {colors['cyan']}{enemy.name}{colors['reset']} attacks and does {colors['red']}{damage}{colors['reset']} damage! ({colors['yellow']}{defense}{colors['reset']} absorbed by armor.)\n", DELAY)
        damage = 0 # empty damage for next round
        
from weapons import *  # import the default weapon for new characters
from armor import * # import default armor for new characters

class Character:
    def __init__(self, name, level=1, gold=5, health=30, xp=0, weapon=marshal, armor=farm_clothes):
        self.name = name
        self.level = level
        self.gold = gold
        self.health = health
        self.max_health = health
        self.xp = xp
        self.weapon = weapon
        self.armor = armor

    def take_damage(self, amount):
        self.health -= amount
        self.health = max(self.health, 0)

    def heal(self, amount):
        self.health += amount
        self.health = min(self.health, self.max_health)

    def gain_gold(self, amount):
        self.gold += amount

    def lose_gold(self, amount):
        self.gold -= amount
        self.gold = max(self.gold, 0)

    def equip_weapon(self, weapon):
        self.weapon = weapon
    
    def equip_armor(self, armor):
        self.armor = armor

    def level_up(self):
        if self.level < 10:
            self.level += 1
            self.max_health = (self.level * 30)
            self.health = self.max_health
            self.xp = 0
        else: 
            self.health = self.max_health
            self.xp = 0
        
    def attack(self, enemy):
        enemy.take_damage(self.weapon.damage)

class Armor:
    def __init__(self, name, level, defense, buy_price, sell_price):
        self.name = name
        self.level = level
        self.defense = defense
        self.buy_price = buy_price
        self.sell_price = sell_price

    def __str__(self):
        return f"Armor: {self.name}\nLevel: {self.level}\nDefense: {self.defense}\nBuy Price: {self.buy_price}\n"

    3: [studded_leather, wool_robe],
    4: [hardened_leather, warm_flannel_robe],
    5: [chain_mail, satin_robe],
    6: [adamantium_armor, silk_robe],
    7: [obsidian_armor, embroidered_silk_robe],
    8: [mithril_armor, velvet_robe],
    9: [dragon_scale_armor, embroidered_velvet_robe],
    10: [celestial_armor, starlight_robe],
    # Add more armors as necessary
}

# Function to get available armors for a level
def get_armors(level):
    armor_list = armor_by_level.get(level, [])
    return armor_list

import os
import random
from ascii_art import *
from characters import Character
from combat import combat, try_healing
from utilities import *
from utilities import menu, cursor_style
from weapons import *
import sys

def main_menu():
    """
    Displays the main menu and prompts the user for an option.

    Returns:
        str: The user's menu choice.
    """
    print(logo)
    print(sword2 + "\n \n")
    print_separator()
    menu("Main Menu", "black_on_yellow")
    print("\n")
    print(f"{colors['yellow']}1{colors['reset']}. New game")
    print(f"{colors['yellow']}2{colors['reset']}. Load game")
    print(f"{colors['yellow']}3{colors['reset']}. Settings menu")
    print(f"{colors['yellow']}4{colors['reset']}. Quit")
    return input("Choose an option: ")

def settings_menu():
    """
    Displays the settings menu and prompts the user for an option.

    Returns:
        str: The user's menu choice.
    """
    print(f"{colors['yellow']}1{colors['reset']}. Change delayed text speed")
    print(f"{colors['yellow']}2{colors['reset']}. Show working directory")
    print(f"{colors['yellow']}3{colors['reset']}. Return")
    return input("Choose an option: ")

def settings(player):
    """
    Displays and handles the settings menu.

    Args:
        player (Character): The player character object.
    """
    clear_screen()
    while True:
        try:
            choice = int(settings_menu())
        except ValueError:
            print("Please enter a valid number.")
            continue
        if choice == 1:
            change_print_speed()
        elif choice == 2:
            print(f"Game data: {working_dir}")
        elif choice == 3:
            break
        else:
            print("Invalid option, please try again.")

def new_game():
    """
    Starts a new game by creating a new player character.

    Returns:
        Character: The new player character object.
    """
    while True:
        try:
            print("\n \n")
            print_separator()
            name = input("A name is a powerful thing. Choose: ").lstrip(' ')
            if len(name) > 1:
                return Character(name)
            else:
                return
        except ValueError:
            print("Nice try, but you still need a name... try again.\n")
            continue
    

def player_choice(player):
    """
    Handles the player's choice in the game menu.

    Args:
        player (Character): The player character object.
    """
    # Default to marshal weapon if no weapon equipped
    if player.weapon is None:
        player.weapon = marshal  

    save_game(player)
    menu("The Dark Forest","white_on_green")
    delay_print("\nWhat do you want to do now?\n", DELAY)
    delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}S{colors['reset']} - Search for enemies\n",DELAY)
    delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}H{colors['reset']} - Heal yourself\n", DELAY)
    delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}R{colors['reset']} - Return to town\n", DELAY)
    delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}Q{colors['reset']} - Quit and save game\n", DELAY)
    while True:
        choice = input(f"Choose an option (S, H, R, Q): ").upper()
        
        if choice == "S":
            n = random.randint(1,20)
            if n < 4:
                sidequest(player,n)
            else:
                clear_screen()
                print(combat_art)
                combat(player)
        elif choice == "H":
            try_healing(player)
        elif choice == "R":
            clear_screen()
            town_menu(player)
            break
        elif choice == "Q":
            quit_game(player)
        elif choice == "X": ################################### 
        #    remove this, testing only    #   ###################################
            xp_percentage = round((player.xp / (player.level * 25)) * 100)
            if xp_percentage < 100:
                xp = int(input("Cheat enabled: New player XP: "))
                player.xp = xp
                print(f"Player experience is now: {player.xp}")
            xp_bar(player)
        elif choice == "Z":  
            print("Cheat enabled: full health.\n")
            player.health = player.max_health
        elif choice == "3":
            sidequest(player, 3)
        else:
            print("Invalid option. Please choose again.")
        

def town_menu(player):
    """
    Displays and handles the town menu.

    Args:
        player (Character): The player character object.
    """
    save_game(player)
    clear_screen()
    print(town)
    menu("Lonesome Raven, Population: 69","black_on_yellow")
    delay_print("\nWhat do you want to do now?\n", DELAY)
    delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}H{colors['reset']} - Visit the healer\n", DELAY)
    delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}G{colors['reset']} - Check out the general store\n", DELAY)
    delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}R{colors['reset']} - Return to the forest\n", DELAY)
    delay_print(f"{colors['yellow']}Q{colors['reset']} - Quit and save game\n", DELAY)
    while True:
        choice = input("Choose an option (H, G, R, Q): ").upper()
        
        if choice == "H":
            visit_healer(player)
            clear_screen()
            town_menu(player)
        elif choice == "G":
            visit_store(player)
            town_menu(player)
        elif choice == "R":
            clear_screen()
            print(forest)
            player_choice(player)
        elif choice == "Q":
            quit_game(player)
        else:
            print("Invalid option. Please choose again.")


def main_game_loop(player):
    """
    Main game loop that handles the gameplay after starting a new game.

    Args:
        player (Character): The player character object.
    """
    clear_screen()
    print(forest) 
    load_strings(working_dir + "/intro.txt")
    print_string("start1")
    print_string("start2")
    print_string("start3")
    print()
    print_separator()
    print()
    
    while True: # display dark forest menu
        display_bars(player)
        player_choice(player)

def main():
    """
    The main function that runs the game.
    """
    clear_screen()
    player = None
    while True:
        try:
            choice = int(main_menu())
        except ValueError:
            print("Please enter a valid number.")
            continue
        if choice == 1:
            player = new_game()
            if player:
                main_game_loop(player)
        elif choice == 2:
            print_separator()
            print(f"Save files to choose from:\n{colors['cyan']}")
            save_files = list_save_files(working_dir)
            for filename in save_files:
                filename = os.path.splitext(filename)[0] # remove extension
                print(filename)
            name = input(f"{colors['reset']}\nEnter character name to load: ")
            
            player = load_game(working_dir + "/" + name + ".sav")
            if player:
                clear_screen()
                display_bars(player)
                player_choice(player)
            else:
                print("Failed to load the game.")
                input("Press enter to continue")
        elif choice == 3:
             settings(player)
        elif choice == 4:
            quit_game(player)
        else:
            print("Invalid option, please try again.")


if __name__ == "__main__":
    cursor_style(3) # blinking underscore cursor
    main()

#!/bin/bash
#
# getwwiv
#

echo "Starting update process"
# Get version info
OS_LABEL='debian10'
WWIV_RELEASE='5.9.0'
OLD_VER=`~/bbs -V`
OLD_BUILD_ID=`echo $OLD_VER | awk -F] '{print $1}' | awk -F. '{print $NF}' | tr -d '\n'`
NEW_BUILD_ID=`wget -qO- http://build.wwivbbs.org/jenkins/job/wwiv/label=linux-${OS_LABEL}/lastSuccessfulBuild/buildNumber`

echo "Old build: $OLD_BUILD_ID"
echo "New build: $NEW_BUILD_ID"

if [[ "$OLD_BUILD_ID" -eq "$NEW_BUILD_ID" ]]
then
    echo "Build is current; nothing to do. Exiting update."
    exit
fi

echo "Stopping wwivd service"
sudo /bin/systemctl stop wwivd

WWIVCFG_PID=$(ps -C wwivconfig  -opid --no-headers)
if [ -z ${WWIVCFG_PID+x} ]
then
    echo "wwivconfig not running"
else
    echo "Stopping wwivconfig"
    kill ${WWIVCFG_PID}
fi

WFC_PID=$(ps -C bbs  -opid,tty,cmd --no-headers | awk '/pts/{print $1}')
if [ -z ${WFC_PID+x} ]
then
    echo "WFC not running"
else
    echo "Stopping WFC"
    kill ${WFC_PID}
fi

echo "Backup current wwiv directory for build ${OLD_BUILD_ID}"
cd /bbs
tar zcf wwiv.${OLD_BUILD_ID}.`date "+%Y%m%d_%H%M%S"`.tgz wwiv

echo "Grabbing current build"
cd /tmp
if [[ -d "/tmp/wwiv" ]]
then
    rm -rf /tmp/wwiv
fi
mkdir wwiv
cd wwiv

wget http://build.wwivbbs.org/jenkins/job/wwiv/label=linux-${OS_LABEL}/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/wwiv-linux-${OS_LABEL}-${WWIV_RELEASE}.${NEW_BUILD_ID}.tar.gz

echo "Extracting new build files"
tar zxf wwiv-linux-${OS_LABEL}-${WWIV_RELEASE}.${NEW_BUILD_ID}.tar.gz

echo "Updating files"
cp -v bbs wwivfsed wwivconfig wwivutil network* wwivd build.nfo whatsnew.txt /bbs/wwiv/

echo "Refreshing zip files"
cp *.zip ${HOME}

echo "Updating gfiles"
cd ${HOME}/gfiles
unzip -uLo /tmp/wwiv/gfiles.zip

echo "Updating scripts"
cd ${HOME}/scripts
unzip -uLo /tmp/wwiv/scripts.zip

cd ${HOME}
# Get new version
NEW_VER=`~/bbs -V`

echo "Starting wwivd service"
sudo /bin/systemctl start wwivd

echo
echo "Update Complete"
echo "Old Version: $OLD_VER"
echo "New Version: $NEW_VER"
echo
